KEDR COI 0.1 released

This is the first public stable version of KEDR COI library. 
Main features of this version:
    * support for flexible interception of callback operations: pre-
    and post-handlers, interception in case when pointer to callback
    operation is NULL;
    * support for automatic watching newly created objects with
    operations copied from another object ('foreign interceptor');
    * already implemented interceptors for objects of types
    'struct file_system_type', 'struct super_block', 'struct inode',
    'struct dentry', 'struct file';
    * easy implementation of interceptors for new types of objects
    with usage of template generation tool.